## Why cats love lilkus

- **Endless play** — toys move randomly to keep cats curious  
- **Engaging sounds** — optional squeaks, bells, and chirps  
- **Bright & bold** — animations designed to catch feline vision  
- **Gentle & safe** — no ads, no distractions, just pure fun  

