## FAQ

**Is it safe for my cat?**  
Yes — lilkus is designed with simple visuals and optional sounds. Just place your device on a flat surface and supervise playtime.  

**Will it scratch my screen?**  
Modern screens are tough! But you can use a screen protector for peace of mind.  

**Does it work on tablets too?**  
Yes — bigger screens = bigger playground 🐾  

